 via AppConfig::Getopt.  E.g. "=i", ":s", "=s@".  This can also be used to 
 implicitly set the ARGCOUNT value (C</^!/> = ARGCOUNT_NONE, C</@/> = 
-ARGCOUNT_LIST, C</%/ = ARGCOUNT_HASH, C</[=:].*/> = ARGCOUNT_ONE)
